OL,3,CLondon hotter than Ibiza on highest
OL,4,Cearly April temperature in 80 years
OL,6,FWednesday was the hottest day recorded
OL,7,Fin the first half of April since 1946,
OL,8,Fthe Met Office said.
OL,10,FA temperature of 26.5C was recorded in
OL,11,FKew Gardens, south west London, making
OL,12,Fit the hottest day of 2026 so far.
OL,14,FIn a statement, the Met Office said:
OL,15,F"Today we have seen 26.5C recorded in
OL,16,FKew Gardens in London, the warmest day
OL,17,Fof the year so far and one of the
OL,18,Fwarmest April days on record."
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@^O]
