OL,3,CLondon hotter than Ibiza on highest
OL,4,Cearly April temperature in 80 years
OL,6,FWednesday's temperature surpassed the
OL,7,F24.8C recorded in Mona on the island
OL,8,Fof Anglesey in Wales on Tuesday `
OL,9,Fwhich was also the hottest April 7 on
OL,10,Frecord.
OL,12,FIt was also hotter than temperatures
OL,13,Frecorded in popular holiday
OL,14,Fdestinations, including Ibiza, Rome
OL,15,Fand Marrakech.
OL,17,FTom Morgan, a meteorologist at the Met
OL,18,FOffice, said: "Temperatures even into
OL,19,Fthe mid 20s are very uncommon at this
OL,20,Ftime of year.
OL,26,@zD@OOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
