PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775671869
OL,3,CLondon hotter than Ibiza on highest
OL,4,Cearly April temperature in 80 years
OL,6,F"In the London area, we've seen
OL,7,Ftemperatures above 26 degrees Celsius,
OL,8,Fand currently the provisional maximum
OL,9,Ftoday is 26.5 Celsius in Kew Gardens,
OL,10,FLondon. And that is pretty exceptional
OL,11,Ffor at least the first half of April.
OL,12,FIt's been very, very warm, but it is a
OL,13,Fbrief peak in the heat, with
OL,14,Ftemperatures for most of the UK
OL,15,Fconsiderably lower tomorrow."
OL,17,FThe hot spell, which began on Monday,
OL,18,Fis far above the early April average
OL,19,Fof 12C to 15C.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@]O]
