PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775671869
OL,3,CLondon hotter than Ibiza on highest
OL,4,Cearly April temperature in 80 years
OL,6,FHowever, Thursday is expected to see
OL,7,Frain and cooler, showery weather
OL,8,Fmoving southeast across the UK.
OL,10,FAs people flocked to the coast in the
OL,11,Fwarm weather, a charity urged people
OL,12,Fto make sure they stay safe when
OL,13,Fcooling off.
OL,15,FDespite the high temperatures, the Met
OL,16,FOffice has said that this week's
OL,17,Fweather does not meet its definition
OL,18,Fof a heatwave, which requires
OL,19,Ftemperatures to exceed regionspecific
OL,20,Fthresholds of 24C and 27C for at least
OL,21,Fthree consecutive days.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
