OL,3,CLondon hotter than Ibiza on highest
OL,4,Cearly April temperature in 80 years
OL,6,FThe hot weather has also coincided
OL,7,Fwith peak pollen season in the UK,
OL,8,Fwith ash and birch pollen levels
OL,9,Fremaining "very high" according to the
OL,10,FMet Office.
